        content: "# Understanding Your Work Style\n\n## Microlearning Module\n\nYour work style is how you naturally process information, manage tasks, and interact with others. Understanding it gives you a practical framework for communicating your needs. Key questions: When am I most focused? How do I prefer to receive instructions? What environment helps me concentrate? How do I process new information (reading, hearing, doing)? What drains me fastest? What restores me? Write a short personal profile and share relevant parts with your team or manager.\n\n## Key takeaway\n\nApply one thing from this module today.\n",
