        content: "# Product Feature Overview\n\n## Microlearning Module\n\nThis module provides an overview of the platform's key features and how to use them. Navigate the toolkit to find scenario guides, employee resources, and manager materials. Use the self service support section to complete self assessments, create alignment plans, and access signposting. Explore the learning pathways to build your knowledge at your own pace. Check the champions hub for peer support resources. Use the audit tool to assess your team or organisation's neuroinclusion maturity. All content is designed to be accessible, practical, and self paced.\n\n## Key takeaway\n\nApply one thing from this module today.\n",
