        content: "# Team Member Overwhelmed Response Guide\n\n## Quick Reference\n\nSigns: withdrawal, visible tension, difficulty responding, emotional responses, going very still or silent. What to do: keep it simple ('Do you need a few minutes?'), offer a quiet space, reduce immediate demands, do not draw attention, do not ask them to explain, stay calm. After: check in privately later, ask what helped and what did not, discuss prevention. Do not expect them to bounce back in five minutes. Recovery takes the time it takes.\n",
