        title: "Performance Concern vs Support Need",
        description: "Before raising performance concerns, check: 1. Have adjustments been discussed? 2. Were expectations communicated clearly and in an accessible format? 3. Is the environment suitable? 4. Has the per...",
        content: "# Performance Concern vs Support Need\n\n## Quick Reference\n\nBefore raising performance concerns, check: 1. Have adjustments been discussed? 2. Were expectations communicated clearly and in an accessible format? 3. Is the environment suitable? 4. Has the person been asked what they need? If the answer to any of these is no, address the support gap first. Performance management without adjustments in place risks discrimination under the Equality Act 2010. Involve HR early.\n",
