        content: "# Adjustment Tracker Template\n\n## Quick Reference\n\nRecord for each team member (with their knowledge and consent): Name, date agreed, adjustments in place (specific detail), review date, outcome of review, any changes made. Keep this document updated. It should follow the person if they change teams or managers. Review every three months or sooner if circumstances change. This is a living document, not a one off form.\n",
