        description: "Card 1: Disclosure. Listen, thank, ask what they need, keep confidential, follow through. Card 2: Overwhelm. Simple offer, quiet space, reduce demands, check in later. Card 3: Adjustments. Open que...",
        content: "# Manager Quick Reference Cards\n\n## Quick Reference\n\nCard 1: Disclosure. Listen, thank, ask what they need, keep confidential, follow through. Card 2: Overwhelm. Simple offer, quiet space, reduce demands, check in later. Card 3: Adjustments. Open question, listen, agree, document, act, review. Card 4: Communication. Specific, clear, one thing at a time, preferred format, check for questions. Card 5: Performance. Check adjustments first. Always. Card 6: Conflict. Check in promptly, offer break, debrief later, review prevention.\n",
