        content: "# Check In Prompts\n\n## Quick Reference\n\nUse these prompts in regular one to ones: 'How have things been since we last spoke?' 'Is there anything about your workload or environment that's not working?' 'Are the adjustments we agreed still helping?' 'Is there anything you need that you haven't asked for?' 'How are you managing your energy at the moment?' 'Is there anything coming up that you're worried about?' Keep check ins brief, consistent, and private.\n",
