        content: "# Routes to Support and Signposting\n\n## Quick Reference\n\nInternal: your manager, HR, occupational health, EAP (employee assistance programme), neurodiversity champions, mental health first aiders, trade union representative. External: Access to Work (gov.uk/access-to-work) for funded adjustments, ACAS (acas.org.uk) for workplace rights advice, National Autistic Society, ADHD Foundation, British Dyslexia Association, Mind for mental health support, Samaritans (116 123) for crisis support. You do not have to navigate this alone.\n",
